    - Improved error handling. The app now shows a proper 404 'Not Found' page for bad URLs (like a wrong action or missing ID) instead of silently redirecting. This makes bugs much easier to find.
    - Made the login URL consistent with the rest of the app (now `?auth&action=login`).
    - Renamed the default action from `startAction` to `indexAction` in all controllers for better consistency.
    - Reordered methods in all classes to follow a standard structure (properties, constructor, public, protected, private).
    - Introduced the `getTableName()` method in the base controller to handle modules where the URL name and table name differ (like 'start' vs 'main_page_posts').
